form:listbox.form:list-source: SELECT CONCAT(`person_surname`, ' ', `person_givenname`, ' (', `person_id`, ')') AS person_info, `id` FROM `persons` ORDER BY `person_surname` ASC, `person_givenname` ASC, `person_id` ASC

Usuń powiązanie z osobą, przedmiot pozostanie jako "bez właściciela"

form:listbox.form:list-source: SELECT CONCAT(`group_id`, ', "', `group_name`, '"') AS group_info, `id` FROM `groups` ORDER BY `group_info`
SELECT CONCAT(`category_id`, ', "', `category_name`, '"') AS category_info, `id` FROM `categories` ORDER BY `category_info`
SELECT CONCAT(`liquidation_id`, ' (', `liquidation_date`, ')') AS liquidation_info, `id` FROM `liquidations` ORDER BY `liquidation_info`
